headline: IBM Just Gave Nvidia Stock Investors Terrible News
summary: An IBM survey suggests that businesses are struggling to achieve acceptable ROIs from AI investments.  Cheaper AI is likely required to successfully scale up the technology.  The trend of affordable AI models running on cheaper hardware does Nvidia no favors.
